Title: Makita UV3200/2 UV3200 Electric Scarifier 1300W 240V MAKUV3200
Description:
The Makita UV3200 Electric Scarifier has 5 working height adjustment settings. Ideal for smaller lawns, helps to keep your lawn healthy. Fitted with large wheels for stable and easy moving. The handle is fitted with a soft grip for increased comfort during use. It also features tool-free knobs for fast assembling, disassembling and folding of the handles.

Specification:

Input Power: 1,300W
No Load Speed: 3,500/min.
Cutting Width: 32cm
Cutting Height: 5 levels, -10 to +10mm
Collection Box: 30 litres
Power Cord Length: 10m
Weight: 12kg
